vely.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Multilingual support:</span>&nbsp;Making the service accessible to a wider range of citizens.</li></ul><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; text-align: justify;\">By working together, we believe the Online General Dairy (GD) service can become a cornerstone of citizen engagement and effective policing in Bangladesh. We are excited to contribute to this transformative journey and witness its positive impact on the lives of Bangladeshi citizens.</p>', 'transforming-citizen-engagement-bangladeshs-online-general-diary-service-1748948781.jpg', 1, '2024-05-05 22:05:00', '2025-06-03 16:06:21', '2025-06-04 11:14:05');
