(1, 1, '67a7b250c0491.png', 'bKash – Transforming ERP- integrated with Accounting with Opus Technology', 'bKash, Bangladesh’s leading mobile financial services provider, is known for revolutionizing digital transactions and financial inclusion. With rapid business expansion,', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">bKash – Transforming ERP- Suppty Chain &amp; Fixed Asset Management integrated with Accounting\r\nSoftware with Opus Technology</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br>bKash, Bangladesh’s leading mobile financial services provider, is known for\r\nrevolutionizing digital transactions and financial inclusion. With rapid\r\nbusiness expansion, bKash required a robust, scalable, and integrated\r\nenterprise solution to streamline financial operations, optimize resource\r\nmanagement, and ensure seamless reporting.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Project Duration<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>December 29, 2013 – April 30, 2014</b><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Challenges &amp; Implementation Complexities<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Opus Technology took on the challenge of implementing\r\nmultiple enterprise modules within a tight timeframe. The project involved\r\novercoming significant implementation hurdles, including:<o:p></o:p></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0in\" type=\"disc\">\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Complex\r\n     Financial Operations (FO):</b> Managing high-volume transactions,\r\n     reconciliations, and financial reporting.<o:p></o:p></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Accounting\r\n     &amp; MIS Integration:</b> Ensuring accuracy, transparency, and real-time\r\n     insights across departments.<o:p></o:p></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Supply\r\n     Chain Management (SCM):</b> Optimizing procurement, inventory, and vendor\r\n     management for operational efficiency.<o:p></o:p></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Fixed\r\n     Asset Management System:</b> Automating asset tracking, depreciation, and\r\n     compliance reporting.<o:p></o:p></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>HR\r\n     &amp; Payroll Management System:</b> Streamlining workforce\r\n     administration, salary processing, and compliance adherence.<o:p></o:p></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Rent\r\n     Module Implementation:</b> Managing rental agreements, lease tracking, and\r\n     financial settlements.<o:p></o:p></li>\r\n</ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Solution &amp; Execution<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Opus Technology deployed a fully integrated, scalable\r\nenterprise solution tailored to bKash’s operational needs. The approach\r\nincluded:<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;\">✔</span> <b>Customization &amp;\r\nIntegration:</b> Developed tailored solutions ensuring seamless integration\r\nacross all modules.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;\">✔</span> <b>Process Automation:</b> Reduced manual\r\ninefficiencies, improving speed and accuracy in financial operations.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;\">✔</span> <b>Scalability &amp; Security:</b> Ensured the\r\nplatform could support bKash’s exponential growth while maintaining high\r\nsecurity standards.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;\">✔</span> <b>Training &amp; Support:</b> Provided extensive\r\ntraining and ongoing support to ensure smooth adoption.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Results &amp; Impact<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚀</span> <b>Operational\r\nEfficiency Boost:</b> Improved financial workflows, reduced processing time,\r\nand enhanced accuracy.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📊</span>\r\n<b>Real-time Data Insights:</b> Strengthened decision-making through automated\r\nMIS and financial reporting.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🔗</span>\r\n<b>Seamless System Integration:</b> Ensured smooth communication between\r\ndifferent modules, eliminating redundancies.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🔒</span>\r\n<b>Enhanced Compliance &amp; Security:</b> Strengthened regulatory compliance\r\nthrough robust financial controls.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Conclusion<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Despite multiple implementation challenges, Opus Technology\r\nsuccessfully delivered a comprehensive enterprise solution, empowering bKash\r\nwith enhanced efficiency, transparency, and scalability. This project\r\nunderscores Opus Technology’s expertise in tackling complex financial and\r\noperational transformations with cutting-edge solutions.<o:p></o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📩</span> <b>Want to optimize\r\nyour enterprise operations?</b> Let’s build the future together! Contact Opus\r\nTechnology today.<o:p></o:p></p>', 'bkash-transforming-erp-financial-operations-with-opus-technology', '2025-02-08 12:14:16', '2025-05-26 08:44:35'),
(2, 2, '67a7b2732b390.png', 'BRAC_CBF_ERP – Empowering Financial Operations with Opus Technology', 'BRAC Climate Bridge Fund (CBF) is an initiative by BRAC, designed to support climate-vulnerable communiti', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><a href=\"https://www.brac.net/program/climate-bridge-fund\" target=\"_new\">BRAC Climate Bridge Fund (CBF)</a> is an initiative by BRAC,\r\ndesigned to support climate-vulnerable communities through sustainable\r\ninterventions. As the program expanded, the need for a robust, integrated\r\nfinancial and operational system became crucial for managing resources\r\nefficiently and ensuring transparency.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Project Duration<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📅</span> <b>June 15, 2020 –\r\nDecember 31, 2020</b><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Challenges &amp; Implementation Complexities<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Opus Technology was entrusted with implementing a\r\ncomprehensive enterprise solution to streamline BRAC CBF’s operations. However,\r\nthe project faced several challenges, including:<o:p></o:p></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0in\" type=\"disc\">\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Accounting\r\n     &amp; Finance:</b> Ensuring accurate financial tracking, grant management,\r\n     and regulatory compliance.<o:p></o:p></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Asset\r\n     Management:</b> Managing and monitoring program assets across multiple\r\n     locations.<o:p></o:p></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>HR\r\n     &amp; Payroll Management:</b> Automating salary processing, compliance\r\n     reporting, and workforce administration.<o:p></o:p></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Inventory\r\n     Management:</b> Efficient tracking of program materials and resources to\r\n     prevent shortages or excess stock.<o:p></o:p></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Program\r\n     Management:</b> Establishing a centralized system to monitor and evaluate\r\n     climate adaptation projects.<o:p></o:p></li>\r\n</ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Solution &amp; Execution<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Opus Technology developed a tailor-made enterprise solution\r\nto address these challenges, ensuring smooth operational flow across all\r\ncritical modules. Our approach included:<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;\">✔</span> <b>Seamless System\r\nIntegration:</b> A unified platform connecting finance, HR, inventory, and\r\nprogram management.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;\">✔</span> <b>Automation &amp; Efficiency:</b> Reduced manual\r\nintervention to enhance data accuracy and process efficiency.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;\">✔</span> <b>Real-time Monitoring &amp; Reporting:</b>\r\nImproved transparency and decision-making with live data insights.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;\">✔</span> <b>Scalability &amp; Security:</b> Ensured the\r\nsystem could support future growth while maintaining high security standards.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;\">✔</span> <b>User Training &amp; Support:</b> Conducted\r\nhands-on training to ensure seamless adoption across teams.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Results &amp; Impact<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚀</span> <b>Improved Financial\r\nTransparency:</b> Streamlined accounting and fund management, reducing\r\ndiscrepancies.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📊</span>\r\n<b>Enhanced Asset &amp; Inventory Control:</b> Optimized tracking and\r\nallocation of resources across programs.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🔗</span>\r\n<b>Efficient Program Management:</b> Enabled real-time monitoring and impact\r\nassessment for climate adaptation initiatives.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">💼</span>\r\n<b>Optimized HR &amp; Payroll Processes:</b> Simplified workforce management,\r\nensuring timely payments and compliance adherence.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Conclusion<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Despite multiple implementation challenges, Opus Technology\r\nsuccessfully delivered an integrated enterprise solution that empowered BRAC\r\nCBF with enhanced operational efficiency, transparency, and scalability. This\r\nproject showcases Opus Technology’s expertise in implementing cutting-edge\r\nsolutions for large-scale non-profit and climate-focused programs.<o:p></o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📩</span> <b>Looking for a\r\nscalable enterprise solution?</b> Let’s innovate together! Contact Opus\r\nTechnology today.<o:p></o:p></p>', 'brac-climate-bridge-fund-empowering-sustainable-financial-operations-with-opus-technology', '2025-02-08 13:07:05', '2025-05-26 08:44:45'),
(3, 43, '6821fcb00701c.png', 'Advancing Citizen Services: Online GD Automation Solutions for Bangladesh Police, PHQ', 'Opus Technology Limited collaborated with Bangladesh Police to develop and deploy an integrated digital platform encompassing Online GD (General Diary) automation, citizen-facing mobile apps, digital duty activity tracking, and unidentified dead body data management. This multi-feature system brings transparency, accessibility, and operational efficiency to public safety services across the nation.', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Implementation of Online GD, Citizen App, Duty Management\r\n&amp; UDB System for Bangladesh Police with Opus Technology</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Case Study: Comprehensive Digital Public Service &amp;\r\nPolice Activity Platform Deployment<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Client:</b> Bangladesh Police<br>\r\n<b>Delivered by:</b> Opus Technology Limited<br>\r\n<b>Client Website:</b> <a href=\"https://www.police.gov.bd/\" target=\"_new\">www.police.gov.bd</a><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Client Overview<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Bangladesh Police is tasked with maintaining public order\r\nand providing essential services to citizens across the country. Traditional\r\nsystems for filing General Diaries (GD), managing daily police duties, and\r\nidentifying unknown deceased persons relied heavily on manual\r\nprocesses—creating inefficiencies, accessibility gaps, and record\r\ninconsistencies. To address this, a unified digital solution was essential for\r\nimproving citizen engagement and internal coordination.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Project Summary<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Opus Technology Limited successfully developed and launched\r\nan end-to-end digital service platform that includes:<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:.75in;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 