riant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><b>Digital Duty Activity Management</b><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:.75in;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nSymbol\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><b>Unidentified Dead Body (UDB) Record System</b><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">This suite of tools modernizes both public-facing and\r\ninternal police operations, making services more accessible, secure, and\r\nefficient.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Key Objectives</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">• Allow citizens to submit General Diaries online securely\r\nand conveniently<br>\r\n• Empower the public with mobile apps for police assistance and service\r\ntracking<br>\r\n• Digitize duty rosters and activity logging for transparency and supervision<br>\r\n• Build a central database for unidentified dead bodies with image and data\r\nrecords<br>\r\n• Reduce manual paperwork and improve service speed<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Challenges<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚫</span> Citizens faced long\r\nqueues and travel burdens to file GDs at police stations<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚫</span>\r\nNo public platform to track the status of filed reports or get updates<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚫</span>\r\nManual duty scheduling lacked transparency and oversight<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚫</span>\r\nFragmented data on unidentified bodies hindered identification and reporting<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Our Solution</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Opus Technology built and implemented a multi-module digital\r\npolicing solution:<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span> <b>Online GD Platform</b> –\r\nWeb-based and mobile GD submission with OTP verification, photo uploads, and\r\nPDF downloads<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<b>Mobile Apps for Citizens</b> – Android and iOS apps for filing GDs,\r\nemergency contacts, police station locators, and push notifications<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<b>Digital Duty Management</b> – Officer assignment scheduling, attendance\r\ntracking, and duty reporting dashboards for supervisors<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<b>Unidentified Dead Body Module</b> – Secure database with image uploads,\r\nbiometric entry (where available), location tagging, and inter-station sharing<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Results &amp; Impact</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span> Increased Accessibility\r\n– Citizens can now file GDs remotely via mobile or web<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span>\r\nFaster Processing – Digital workflows reduce delays in registering and\r\nverifying reports<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span>\r\nEnhanced Duty Oversight – Real-time monitoring of officer deployment and\r\naccountability<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span>\r\nBetter Identification – Improved public visibility of UDB records facilitates\r\nfamily tracing<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span>\r\nCitizen Engagement – Mobile apps strengthen communication between police and\r\nthe public<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Conclusion</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">By deploying the <b>Online GD Automation System</b>, <b>Citizen\r\nMobile Apps</b>, <b>Digital Duty Management</b>, and <b>Unidentified Dead Body\r\nPlatform</b>, Opus Technology has enabled Bangladesh Police to adopt a\r\nforward-thinking approach to law enforcement services. The integrated system\r\nreflects a national commitment to smart policing, public accessibility, and\r\ndigital governance.<o:p></o:p></p><div class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\">\r\n\r\n<hr size=\"2\" width=\"100%\" align=\"center\">\r\n\r\n</div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">💡</span> <b>Opus Technology –\r\nBridging Communities and Law Enforcement Through Innovation</b> <span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📱🛡️📋</span><o:p></o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>', 'advancing-citizen-services-online-gd-digital-duty-solutions-for-bangladesh-police', '2025-05-06 14:56:29', '2025-05-26 08:57:52'),
(4, 4, '67a7b3c95794c.png', 'IFRC Bangladesh–Streamlining HR & Payroll Mgt. with Opus Technology', 'The International Federation of Red Cross and Red Crescent Societies (IFRC) – Bangladesh Delegation is a', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The <b>International Federation of Red Cross and Red\r\nCrescent Societies (IFRC) – Bangladesh Delegation</b> is a key humanitarian\r\norganization supporting disaster response, health services, and community\r\nresilience programs. To enhance operational efficiency, IFRC Bangladesh\r\nrequired a <b>comprehensive HR &amp; Payroll management system</b> to\r\nstreamline workforce administration and payroll processing.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Project Duration<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📅</span> <b>October 24, 2019 –\r\nDecember 24, 2019</b><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Challenges &amp; Implementation Complexities<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Opus Technology was tasked with developing an integrated HRM\r\n&amp; Payroll solution within a tight timeline. The project faced several\r\nchallenges, including:<o:p></o:p></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0in\" type=\"disc\">\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Complex\r\n     Payroll Processing:</b> Managing multi-tier salary structures, allowances,\r\n     and deductions for a large workforce.<o:p></o:p></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Regulatory\r\n     Compliance:</b> Ensuring adherence to local labor laws and tax\r\n     regulations.<o:p></o:p></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Employee\r\n     Records &amp; Attendance Management:</b> Automating leave tracking,\r\n     performance management, and contract renewals.<o:p></o:p></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Data\r\n     Security &amp; Access Control:</b> Protecting sensitive employee data\r\n     while ensuring controlled access.<o:p></o:p></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Integ