(5, 37, '6821fc44aa1a3.png', 'AI-Powered Assistance: Chatbot Deployment for PHQ Help Desk of Bangladesh Police, Dhaka', 'Opus Technology developed and installed an AI-driven chatbot for the Police Headquarters (PHQ) Help Desk of Bangladesh Police, automating public inquiries, improving service response times, and enabling 24/7 support through a secure digital interface.', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Case Study: Chatbot Development &amp; Installation for\r\nthe PHQ Help Desk</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Client:</b> Bangladesh Police – Police Headquarters (PHQ)<br>\r\n<b>Delivered by:</b> Opus Technology Limited<br>\r\n<b>Client Website:</b> <a href=\"https://www.police.gov.bd/\" target=\"_new\">https://www.police.gov.bd</a><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Client Overview<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Police Headquarters (PHQ) serves as the central\r\nadministrative and communication hub for the Bangladesh Police. The PHQ Help\r\nDesk receives a high volume of public inquiries, including information\r\nrequests, complaints, service guidance, and updates. Traditionally, this\r\nworkload was handled manually via calls and physical visits, often causing\r\ndelays, repetitive responses, and service inefficiencies.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">To improve public engagement and reduce manual burden, PHQ\r\naimed to deploy a smart, automated chatbot solution capable of providing\r\ninstant, reliable, and round-the-clock assistance to citizens and internal\r\nstaff.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Project Summary</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Opus Technology Limited designed, developed, and deployed an\r\nintelligent chatbot integrated with the PHQ Help Desk\'s digital infrastructure.\r\nThe chatbot responds to frequently asked questions, guides users through\r\nservices, and redirects complex queries to human agents when necessary—all via\r\nan intuitive web and mobile-friendly interface.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Key Objectives</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">• Provide 24/7 automated assistance for common public\r\nqueries<br>\r\n• Reduce manual workload on PHQ Help Desk staff<br>\r\n• Ensure timely, consistent, and accurate responses<br>\r\n• Improve public accessibility and satisfaction through digital tools<br>\r\n• Support bilingual communication (Bangla &amp; English) for wider reach<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Challenges</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚫</span> Overloaded help desk\r\nwith repetitive and high-volume inquiries<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚫</span>\r\nLimited-service hours causing delays in public response<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚫</span>\r\nInconsistent responses due to manual handling<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚫</span>\r\nLack of digital channels for instant communication<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Our Solution<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Opus Technology deployed a secure, conversational chatbot\r\nsystem with:<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span> <b>Natural Language Processing\r\n(NLP)</b> – Understands and responds in Bangla and English<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<b>Pre-Programmed Knowledge Base</b> – Covers FAQs, services, procedures, and\r\ncontact details<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<b>Live Chat Handoff</b> – Transfers unresolved queries to human operators<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<b>Mobile &amp; Web Integration</b> – Accessible via smartphones and the\r\nofficial website<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<b>Data Logging &amp; Analytics</b> – Tracks usage patterns, query types, and\r\nresponse accuracy<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<b>Scalable Architecture</b> – Ready to integrate with future police service\r\nportals and databases<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Results &amp; Impact</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span> <b>24/7 Public Support</b>\r\n– Citizens can get answers instantly at any hour<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span>\r\n<b>Reduced Manual Load</b> – Help Desk staff focus on complex or sensitive\r\ninquiries<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span>\r\n<b>Improved Service Consistency</b> – Standardized responses enhance\r\ncredibility<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span>\r\n<b>Higher Engagement</b> – Increased interaction through easy-to-use digital\r\nplatform<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span>\r\n<b>Real-Time Insights</b> – Dashboard helps track public needs and improve\r\nservices<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Conclusion</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">The installation of a chatbot at the PHQ Help Desk marks a\r\nmajor step forward in digital governance for Bangladesh Police. Developed by\r\nOpus Technology, this solution enhances public service delivery, supports\r\nautomation, and strengthens the interface between citizens and law enforcement.<o:p></o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">💡</span> <b>Opus Technology –\r\nBridging Citizens &amp; Institutions Through Intelligent Digital Solutions</b> <span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">💬🤖📞</span><o:p></o:p></p>', 'ai-powered-assistance-chatbot-deployment-for-phq-help-desk-of-bangladesh-police-police-headquarters-dhaka', '2025-05-10 16:08:42', '2025-05-26 09:27:20'),
(6, 9, '67a7b437e5704.png', 'Agrani Bank PLC – Implementing Real-Time Gross Settlement (RTGS) with Opus Technology', 'Agrani Bank PLC is one of Bangladesh’s leading state-owned commercial banks, providing financial services to millions.', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><a href=\"https://www.agranibank.org/\" target=\"_new\">Agrani\r\nBank PLC</a> is one of Bangladesh’s leading state-owned commercial banks,\r\nproviding financial services to millions. To enhance transaction efficiency and\r\ncomply with Bangladesh Bank’s digital banking initiatives, Agrani Bank required\r\nthe implementation of a <b>Real-Time Gross Settlement (RTGS) module</b> for\r\nsecure and instant interbank transactions.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Project Duration<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📅</span> <b>January 7, 2019 –\r\nSeptember 10, 2019</b><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Challenges &amp; Implementation Complexities<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Opus Technology was entrusted with deploying the RTGS module\r\nwithin Agrani Bank’s core banking infrastructure. However, the project\r\nencountered several challenges, including:<o:p></o:p></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0in\" type=\"disc\">\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>System\r\n     Integration with Core Banking:</b> Ensuring seamless connectivity between\r\n     RTGS and existing banking operations.<o:p></o:p></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Real-Time\r\n     Transaction Processing:</b> Enabling high-speed, error-free fund transfers\r\n     with zero delays.<o:p></o:p></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Regulatory\r\n     Compliance:</b> Adhering to Bangladesh Bank’s guidelines and security\r\n     standards for RTGS transactions.<o:p></o:p></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Scalability\r\n     &amp; Performance:</b> Handling high transaction volumes without impacting\r\n     banking operations.<o:p></o:p></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>User\r\n     Training &amp; Adoption:</b> Ensuring bank staff could effectively operate\r\n     and manage the new system.<o:p></o:p></li>\r\n</ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Solution &amp; Execution<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Opus Technology successfully designed and deployed a <b>custom\r\nRTGS module</b>, ensuring efficient and secure transaction processing. Our\r\napproach included:<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;\">✔</span> <b>Seamless Core Banking\r\nIntegration:</b> Enabled real-time fund transfers between financial\r\ninstitutions.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;\">✔</span> <b>Automated Transaction Processing:</b> Eliminated\r\nmanual errors and reduced settlement delays.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;\">✔</span> <b>Regulatory Compliance Assurance:</b> Aligned the\r\nsystem with Bangladesh Bank’s RTGS framework.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;\">✔</span> <b>Scalable &amp; Secure Architecture:</b> Built a\r\nhigh-performance platform to handle increasing transaction volumes.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;\">✔</span> <b>Comprehensive User Training &amp; Support:</b>\r\nProvided training sessions for bank employees to ensure smooth adoption.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Results &amp; Impact<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚀</span> <b>Faster &amp; Secure\r\nTransactions:</b> Enabled instant, error-free interbank settlements.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📊</span>\r\n<b>Enhanced Banking Efficiency:</b> Reduced transaction processing time and\r\noperational workload.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🔗</span>\r\n<b>Seamless Core Banking Integration:</b> Ensured smooth financial operations\r\nwithout disruptions.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🔒</span>\r\n<b>Regulatory &amp; Security Compliance:</b> Strengthened financial security in\r\nalignment with central bank regulations.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Conclusion<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Opus Technology successfully implemented the <b>RTGS module</b>\r\nfor Agrani Bank PLC, ensuring real-time, secure, and compliant fund transfers.\r\nThis project highlights our expertise in <b>banking technology solutions</b>,\r\nenabling financial institutions to embrace digital transformation.<o:p></o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📩</span> <b>Looking to modernize\r\nyour banking operations?</b> Let’s innovate together! Contact Opus Technology\r\ntoday.<o:p></o:p></p>', 'agrani-bank-plc-implementing-real-time-gross-settlement-rtgs-with-opus-technology', '2025-02-09 01:44:55', '2025-05-26 09:11:37'),
(7, 34, '6821fc50af6dd.png', 'Mobile-Driven Efficiency: Inventory Management Apps Deployment for Bangladesh Police, PHQ', 'Bangladesh Police Headquarters partnered with Opus Technology to develop and deploy a mobile application for its Inventory Management System, enabling real-time tracking, verification, and control of police assets across departments.', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Case Study: Mobile Application for Inventory Management\r\nSystem of Bangladesh Police, Police Headquarters, PHQ</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Client:</b> Bangladesh Police – Police Headquarters (PHQ)<br>\r\n<b>Delivered by:</b> Opus Technology Limited<br>\r\n<b>Client Website:</b> <a href=\"https://www.police.gov.bd/\" target=\"_new\">https://www.police.gov.bd</a><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Client Overview</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">The Police Headquarters of\r\nBangladesh Police oversees the allocation, usage, and maintenance of equipment\r\nand supplies across the country. From uniforms and communication devices to\r\nvehicles and tactical gear, managing these resources efficiently is vital for\r\noperational readiness.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">The legacy inventory system,\r\nthough functional on desktop, lacked mobility and field-level accessibility,\r\nleading to data entry delays, verification challenges, and manual tracking\r\nissues. A mobile application was needed to provide real-time inventory oversight,\r\nespecially from remote units and stations.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Project Summary</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Opus Technology developed a\r\nsecure, feature-rich mobile application that integrates seamlessly with the\r\nexisting Inventory Management System of Bangladesh Police. The app empowers\r\nfield officers and logistics personnel to update stock information, perform\r\nasset audits, verify item status, and monitor inventory movements from any\r\nlocation.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Key Objectives</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">• Enable real-time inventory access and updates via mobile\r\ndevices<br>\r\n• Minimize manual paperwork and delays in stock tracking<br>\r\n• Allow on-site item verification and reporting from field units<br>\r\n• Ensure data synchronization with the central inventory system<br>\r\n• Improve accountability, transparency, and asset utilization<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Challenges</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚫</span> Delayed updates due to\r\nmanual data entry and limited system access<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚫</span>\r\nInaccurate or outdated records from decentralized tracking<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚫</span>\r\nLack of mobility restricted field-level reporting and auditing<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚫</span>\r\nDifficulty in identifying asset misuse, shortages, or surpluses<span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Our Solution<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Opus Technology delivered a cross-platform mobile\r\napplication with the following features:<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span> <b>Live Stock View &amp; Status\r\nUpdates</b> – Real-time inventory details at department and item level<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<b>QR/Barcode Scanning</b> – Instant identification and audit of inventory\r\nitems<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<b>Asset Verification Tools</b> – On-site validation during transfers,\r\ninspections, or deployments<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<b>Offline Mode &amp; Auto-Sync</b> – Field use without internet; syncs data\r\nonce reconnected<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<b>Role-Based Access Control</b> – Secure login and permission-based task\r\nallocation<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<b>Integrated Dashboard &amp; Reporting</b> – Mobile access to summaries,\r\nshortages, and movement logs<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Results &amp; Impact<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span> <b>Improved Inventory\r\nAccuracy</b> – Reduced data mismatches and loss due to real-time syncing<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span>\r\n<b>Faster Field Operations</b> – On-the-go updates minimized administrative\r\nbottlenecks<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span>\r\n<b>Enhanced Asset Visibility</b> – Full traceability of high-value equipment\r\nand stock<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span>\r\n<b>Stronger Accountability</b> – Real-time data helps identify irregularities\r\nand enforce discipline<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span>\r\n<b>Operational Efficiency</b> – Seamless coordination between stores,\r\nlogistics, and field units<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Conclusion<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">By launching a mobile-enabled\r\nInventory Management System, Bangladesh Police has taken a significant step\r\ntoward smarter logistics and resource control. Opus Technology’s mobile app\r\nempowers officers to manage and monitor inventory anytime, anywhere—ensuring\r\ntransparency, speed, and operational excellence.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">💡</span> <b>Opus Technology –\r\nDriving Efficiency with Mobile Innovation for Public Sector Operations</b> <span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📱📦🛡️</span><o:p></o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>', 'mobile-driven-efficiency-inventory-management-application-deployment-for-bangladesh-police-phq', '2025-05-10 16:02:10', '2025-05-26 09:26:02');
