(13, 13, '67adc1128e5eb.png', 'Investment Corporation of Bangladesh – Transforming HR & Payroll Management with Opus Technology', 'The Investment Corporation of Bangladesh (ICB) is a leading financial institution that plays a crucial role in the country’s capital market development. Managing a large workforce with diverse HR and payroll requirements, ICB needed a robust, scalable, and automated solution to streamline its HR operations efficiently.', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Case Study: Investment Corporation of Bangladesh –\r\nTransforming HR &amp; Payroll Management with Opus Technology<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Client Overview<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Investment Corporation of Bangladesh (ICB) is a leading\r\nfinancial institution that plays a crucial role in the country’s capital market\r\ndevelopment. Managing a large workforce with diverse HR and payroll\r\nrequirements, ICB needed a robust, scalable, and automated solution to\r\nstreamline its HR operations efficiently.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Project Duration<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📅</span> Mar 11, 2024 – December\r\n15, 2024<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Challenges<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🔹</span> Manual &amp;\r\nTime-Consuming Processes – HR and payroll management relied on legacy systems,\r\nleading to inefficiencies.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🔹</span>\r\nCompliance &amp; Accuracy Issues – Ensuring compliance with financial\r\nregulations and labor laws was complex.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🔹</span>\r\nEmployee Self-Service Needs – Lack of a centralized system for employees to\r\naccess their payroll and HR information.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🔹</span>\r\nScalability &amp; Security – The existing system was not scalable to support\r\nfuture growth and lacked modern security measures.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Opus Technology’s Solution<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Opus Technology implemented a customized HR &amp; Payroll\r\nManagement System, designed to automate and streamline key HR functions,\r\nensuring efficiency and compliance.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span> Automated Payroll Processing –\r\nEliminated manual errors and ensured timely salary disbursement.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\nRegulatory Compliance – Integrated tax, provident fund, and other compliance\r\nmodules.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\nEmployee Self-Service Portal – Empowered employees with access to payroll,\r\nleave management, and HR requests.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\nScalable &amp; Secure – Built on a secure, cloud-based infrastructure for\r\nfuture growth.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\nSeamless Integration – Integrated with existing financial systems for smooth\r\ndata flow.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Results &amp; Impact<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span> 50% Reduction in HR\r\nProcessing Time – Faster payroll calculations and approvals.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🔍</span>\r\nEnhanced Accuracy &amp; Compliance – Reduced errors and ensured regulatory\r\nalignment.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">👩‍💻</span>\r\nImproved Employee Experience – Self-service portal increased engagement and\r\naccessibility.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🔒</span>\r\nStronger Data Security – Secure authentication and data encryption ensured\r\nconfidentiality.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Conclusion<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">With Opus Technology’s HR &amp; Payroll Management Solution,\r\nICB successfully transformed its workforce operations, making them more efficient,\r\ncompliant, and employee-friendly. This digital transformation highlights the\r\npower of technology in optimizing HR functions for financial institutions.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📌</span> Looking to modernize\r\nyour HR &amp; Payroll operations? Let’s connect!<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">#OpusTechnology #DigitalTransformation #HRTech\r\n#PayrollManagement #Innovation #ICB<o:p></o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>', 'investment-corporation-of-bangladesh-transforming-hr-payroll-management-with-opus-technology', '2025-02-13 15:53:22', '2025-05-26 08:47:49'),
(14, 22, '6821fcb1dd138.png', 'Securing Entrances: Visitor Management Software & Accessory Deployment at PHQ & Special Branch', 'Opus Technology Limited partnered with Bangladesh Police to implement a smart Visitor Management Software (VMS) at Police Headquarters (PHQ) and Special Branch (SB), complete with essential accessories. The solution automates visitor registration, enhances security screening, and ensures controlled access—strengthening the entry management process at two of the country’s most sensitive law enforcement facilities.', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Implementation of Visitor Management Software for PHQ\r\n&amp; Special Branch with Opus Technology</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Case Study: Visitor Access Control System Deployment for\r\nHigh-Security Police Installations<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Client:</b> Bangladesh Police – Police Headquarters &amp;\r\nSpecial Branch<br>\r\n<b>Delivered by:</b> Opus Technology Limited<br>\r\n<b>Client Website:</b> <a href=\"https://www.police.gov.bd/\" target=\"_new\">www.police.gov.bd</a><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Client Overview</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">The <b>Police Headquarters (PHQ)</b>\r\nand <b>Special Branch (SB)</b> of the <b>Bangladesh Police</b> are key\r\nadministrative and intelligence divisions responsible for critical national\r\nsecurity operations. These offices receive a high volume of external visitors,\r\nstakeholders, and officials. Previously, manual visitor registration posed\r\nrisks of delays, inaccurate records, and inadequate access control. A modern\r\ndigital visitor management solution was necessary to ensure real-time\r\nmonitoring, security compliance, and traceability.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Project Summary</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Opus Technology Limited\r\nsuccessfully delivered a complete <b>Visitor Management System</b> (VMS)\r\nsolution, including both software and physical accessories. The system replaced\r\ntraditional logbooks with a digital platform that registers, verifies, and\r\ntracks visitors in real-time, supported by hardware like biometric scanners, ID\r\nprinters, web cameras, and access control devices.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Key Objectives</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">• Digitize visitor registration and check-in/check-out\r\nprocesses<br>\r\n• Enhance identity verification and reduce unauthorized access risks<br>\r\n• Maintain a searchable digital log of all visitor interactions<br>\r\n• Improve entry efficiency without compromising security protocols<br>\r\n• Integrate physical devices for seamless visitor data capture and control<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Challenges</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚫</span> Manual logbooks lacked\r\nverification and real-time tracking<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚫</span>\r\nNo central visitor database for monitoring and analytics<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚫</span>\r\nDifficult to identify repeat or blacklisted visitors<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚫</span>\r\nCumbersome entry procedures created delays and vulnerabilities<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Our Solution</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Opus Technology deployed an integrated <b>Visitor Management\r\nSoftware</b> with supporting hardware, including:<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span> <b>Digital Visitor Registration\r\nSystem</b> – Captures visitor name, photo, contact details, and purpose of\r\nvisit<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<b>Biometric Scanners &amp; ID Card Printers</b> – Instant ID generation and\r\nidentity validation<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<b>Web Camera Integration</b> – Photo capture at registration for\r\nrecord-keeping and badge printing<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<b>Access Control Devices</b> – Optional integration with doors/gates for\r\nsecure area entry<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<b>Real-Time Dashboard</b> – Monitor check-ins and check-outs across both PHQ\r\nand SB<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<b>Centralized Visitor Log</b> – Searchable visitor history with date, time,\r\nand visit details<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Results &amp; Impact</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span> Increased Security –\r\nVerified, traceable records of every visitor entry and exit<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span>\r\nFaster Check-Ins – Streamlined process reduced wait times at entry points<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span>\r\nReal-Time Monitoring – Central control room oversight of all visitor movements<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span>\r\nImproved Data Accuracy – Eliminated errors from handwritten logs<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span>\r\nScalable &amp; Future-Proof – Ready for expansion to other police installations<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Conclusion</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">The deployment of the <b>Visitor Management Software with\r\naccessories</b> at <b>PHQ</b> and <b>Special Branch</b> has significantly\r\nmodernized visitor oversight for Bangladesh Police. With improved security,\r\nefficiency, and traceability, Opus Technology’s solution supports safer and\r\nsmarter access control at critical national facilities.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 1rem; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\">💡</span><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"> </span><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Opus Technology –\r\nSmart Security Solutions for Safer Institutions</b><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 1rem; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\">🛡️📋</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>', 'securing-entrances-visitor-management-software-accessory-deployment-at-phq-special-branch', '2025-05-06 14:41:10', '2025-05-26 09:17:28'),
(16, 15, '67adc76e1a8c2.png', 'CRAB – Transforming CRO, CRM, Accounting, HR & Payroll Management with Opus Technology', 'Credit Rating Agency of Bangladesh (CRAB) is a leading credit rating institution that plays a crucial role in financial risk assessment across various industries. To maintain accuracy, efficiency, and regulatory compliance, CRAB required a fully integrated digital solution to modernize its Credit Rating Operations, Customer Relationship Management (CRM), Accounting, and HR & Payroll Management.', '<h3 data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"129\" style=\"text-align: justify; \"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Case Study: CRAB – Transforming Credit Rating Operations,\r\nCRM, Accounting, HR &amp; Payroll Management with Opus Technology</b></h3>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Client Overview<o:p></o:p></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Credit Rating Agency of Bangladesh (CRAB)</b> is a\r\nleading credit rating institution that plays a crucial role in financial risk\r\nassessment across various industries. To maintain accuracy, efficiency, and\r\nregulatory compliance, CRAB required a <b>fully integrated digital solution</b>\r\nto modernize its <b>Credit Rating Operations, Customer Relationship Management\r\n(CRM), Accounting, and HR &amp; Payroll Management</b>.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Challenges<o:p></o:p></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1rem; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\">🔹</span><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"> </span><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Manual Credit Rating\r\nProcesses</b><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"> – Inefficiencies in data collection, risk assessment, and report\r\ngeneration.</span></div>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\"><div style=\"text-align