(20, 48, '6821fc8f05092.png', 'Modernizing Law Enforcement Intelligence: CDMS++ Upgradation & Maintenance for Bangladesh, PHQ', 'Opus Technology successfully upgraded and initiated ongoing maintenance for the Crime Data Management System (CDMS++) at Bangladesh Police Headquarters, enhancing system performance, data integrity, and real-time analytics to support smarter policing.', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Case Study: Upgradation &amp; Maintenance of Crime Data\r\nManagement System (CDMS++) for Enhanced Police Intelligence, Bangladesh Police, Police Headquarters, PHQ</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Client:</b> Bangladesh Police – Police Headquarters (PHQ)<br>\r\n<b>Delivered by:</b> Opus Technology Limited<br>\r\n<b>Client Website:</b> <a href=\"https://www.police.gov.bd/\" target=\"_new\">https://www.police.gov.bd</a><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Client Overview</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Police Headquarters (PHQ) of Bangladesh Police oversees\r\nnational law enforcement operations, data-driven investigations, and public\r\nsafety initiatives. The Crime Data Management System (CDMS++) is a\r\nmission-critical platform that collects, stores, and analyzes crime reports and\r\ncase progress from all over the country.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">With growing data volume and increasing demand for faster\r\nanalysis, the legacy CDMS++ needed a comprehensive upgrade and continuous\r\nmaintenance to improve system responsiveness, integration, and user experience\r\nwhile ensuring secure access and compliance with law enforcement protocols.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Project Summary</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Opus Technology Limited led the modernization of the CDMS++\r\nthrough core system upgrades, database optimization, interface redesign, and\r\nimplementation of real-time reporting features. The project also included\r\nestablishing a dedicated maintenance framework to ensure long-term performance,\r\nsecurity, and technical support.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Key Objectives</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">• Enhance system performance and reduce data processing lag<br>\r\n• Upgrade outdated modules and optimize the backend database<br>\r\n• Strengthen data security and user access management<br>\r\n• Improve reporting, analytics, and decision-making tools<br>\r\n• Provide long-term system maintenance and technical support<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Challenges</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚫</span> Outdated architecture\r\nlimited system scalability and speed<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚫</span>\r\nSecurity vulnerabilities due to legacy code and access controls<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚫</span>\r\nDifficulties generating real-time reports for decision-makers<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚫</span>\r\nLimited user interface flexibility and outdated design standards<span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Our Solution<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Opus Technology delivered a comprehensive CDMS++ upgrade and\r\nmaintenance solution featuring:<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span> <b>System Optimization &amp;\r\nModernization</b> – Updated core software, improved system performance<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,san