(46, 46, '67b6ef674ed60.png', 'Digital Transformation of ERP Software Solution-Club & Others of National Press Club, Bangladesh', 'The National Press Club, a prestigious hub for journalists, required a modernized Restaurant Management, Club Management, and Member Management System, along with POS Machine, Bar Code Register, and Scanner Software to streamline operations, enhance member experience, and improve financial management.', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Case Study: Digital Transformation of ERP Software Solution of National Press Club\r\nwith Opus Technology<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Client Overview<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">The <b>National Press Club</b>, a\r\nprestigious hub for journalists, required a modernized <b>Restaurant\r\nManagement, Club Management, and Member Management System</b>, along with <b>POS\r\nMachine, Bar Code Register, and Scanner Software</b> to streamline operations,\r\nenhance member experience, and improve financial management.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Challenges<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚀</span> Manual and\r\ntime-consuming restaurant and club management processes<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚀</span>\r\nDifficulty in tracking member activities, subscriptions, and billing<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚀</span>\r\nLack of an integrated POS system for seamless transactions<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚀</span>\r\nInefficient inventory and sales tracking without barcode integration<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Our Solution<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Opus Technology designed and implemented a <b>comprehensive,\r\nfully integrated management system</b>, providing:<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span> <b>Restaurant Management</b> –\r\nEfficient order processing, kitchen coordination, and billing automation.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<b>Club Management</b> – Streamlined event bookings, activity tracking, and\r\nfacility management.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<b>Member Management</b> – Automated member registration, subscription renewal,\r\nand access control.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<b>POS Machine Integration</b> – Fast and secure transactions with real-time\r\ndata synchronization.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<b>Bar Code Register &amp; Scanner</b> – Accurate inventory tracking and\r\nhassle-free billing.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Results &amp; Impact<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span> <b>Enhanced Operational\r\nEfficiency</b> – Reduced manual workload and improved service speed.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span>\r\n<b>Seamless Member Experience</b> – Easy access, billing, and facility usage\r\ntracking.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span>\r\n<b>Improved Financial Transparency</b> – Real-time revenue tracking and\r\nfinancial reporting.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span>\r\n<b>Scalable &amp; Future-Ready</b> – A robust system capable of adapting to\r\nfuture expansions.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Conclusion<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Opus Technology’s end-to-end\r\ndigital solution has <b>transformed the National Press Club\'s management</b>,\r\nenabling seamless operations, better member services, and improved financial\r\noversight. This implementation marks a significant step toward a <b>smarter,\r\ntechnology-driven future</b> for club and restaurant management.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">💡</span> <b>Opus Technology –\r\nPowering Digital Innovation in Restaurant, Member Management, POS Machine\r\nIntegration &amp; Club Management!</b> <span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚀</span><o:p></o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>', 'digital-transformation-of-erp-software-solution-of-national-press-club-with-opus-technology', '2025-02-20 15:01:27', '2025-05-26 09:19:16'),
(47, 31, '6821fc686a973.png', 'Smart Communication Upgrade: IP Phone Phonebook Management App Deployment for PHQ', 'Bangladesh Police Headquarters deployed an IP Phone Phonebook App developed by Opus Technology to streamline internal communication, enabling fast, secure, and centralized contact access across departments.', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Case Study: Centralized IP Phone Directory App for Secure\r\nPolice Communication</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Client:</b> Bangladesh Police – Police Headquarters (PHQ)<br>\r\n<b>Delivered by:</b> Opus Technology Limited<br>\r\n<b>Client Website:</b> <a href=\"https://www.police.gov.bd/\" target=\"_new\">https://www.police.gov.bd</a><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Client Overview</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">The Police Headquarters (PHQ) of\r\nBangladesh Police coordinates thousands of officers and staff across multiple\r\ndepartments and divisions. Effective communication is critical for operational\r\nefficiency, coordination, and emergency response. However, maintaining\r\nup-to-date contact information across manual directories or paper-based lists\r\nresulted in delays, outdated information, and inefficiencies.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">To overcome these limitations,\r\nPHQ required a digital IP Phone Phonebook App integrated with their existing\r\ncommunication systems, enabling officers to quickly access verified contact\r\ndetails and make secure internal calls.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Project Summary</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Opus Technology Limited designed\r\nand implemented a custom IP Phone Phonebook App tailored for the Bangladesh\r\nPolice PHQ. The solution offers a secure, searchable, and role-based directory\r\nsystem compatible with the IP telephony infrastructure used by the force.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">The app supports mobile and\r\ndesktop access, empowering authorized personnel to quickly find and call\r\ncolleagues using an updated internal phonebook.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Key Objectives</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">• Centralize internal phonebook data for all departments<br>\r\n• Enable fast search and direct dialing from within the app<br>\r\n• Maintain up-to-date contact details with admin-level editing rights<br>\r\n• Improve internal coordination during operations or emergencies<br>\r\n• Secure access to communication tools via role-based authentication<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Challenges</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚫</span> Paper-based phonebooks\r\nwere quickly outdated and hard to update<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚫</span>\r\nDifficulty in finding accurate contact details in real-time<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚫</span>\r\nCommunication delays during critical coordination moments<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚫</span>\r\nNo centralized digital system for IP phone contact management<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Our Solution</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Opus Technology delivered a user-friendly, scalable IP Phone\r\nPhonebook App with the following features:<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span> <b>Centralized Directory\r\nManagement</b> – Maintains verified contact info for all PHQ departments<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<b>Advanced Search Functionality</b> – Instantly find contacts by name, rank,\r\nor department<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<b>Click-to-Call Integration</b> – Direct dialing through the app linked with\r\nIP phone systems<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<b>Role-Based Access</b> – Admins can manage, add, or update contact records<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<b>Multi-Platform Support</b> – Accessible on desktop browsers and mobile\r\ndevices<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<b>Secure Login &amp; Access Logs</b> – Ensures traceability and protection of\r\nsensitive data<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Results &amp; Impact</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span> <b>Faster Internal\r\nCommunication</b> – Officers can locate and contact colleagues within seconds<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span>\r\n<b>Improved Information Accuracy</b> – Central database eliminates outdated\r\nrecords<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span>\r\n<b>Operational Efficiency</b> – Streamlined coordination across all PHQ\r\ndivision