(53, 51, '6821fc36750ca.png', 'Digitizing Web-Based Store Mgt. Software for Bangladesh Police Academy, Sardah', 'Bangladesh Police Academy, Sardah, partnered with Opus Technology to implement and customize a web-based Store Management Software, enabling centralized stock control, real-time tracking, and greater transparency in managing academy supplies and equipment.', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Case Study: Implementation &amp; Customization of Store\r\nManagement Software for Bangladesh Police Academy, Sardah</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Client:</b> Bangladesh Police Academy – Sardah, Rajshahi<br>\r\n<b>Delivered by:</b> Opus Technology Limited<br>\r\n<b>Client Website:</b> <a href=\"https://www.police.gov.bd/\" target=\"_new\">https://www.police.gov.bd</a><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Client Overview</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Bangladesh Police Academy, located in Sardah, Rajshahi, is\r\nthe premier training institution for police officers across the country. The\r\nacademy manages a vast array of training materials, uniforms, equipment, and\r\ndaily operational supplies. Previously reliant on manual stockkeeping, the\r\nacademy faced delays, tracking issues, and inconsistent records in managing its\r\nlogistics.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">To improve efficiency and ensure accountability, the academy\r\nrequired a centralized, web-based store management solution customized to its\r\nunique needs.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Project Summary</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Opus Technology Limited successfully implemented a web-based\r\nStore Management Software tailored to the academy’s structure. The platform\r\ndigitized all store operations, from procurement tracking to item issuance,\r\nallowing seamless access and reporting from any authorized location.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Key Objectives</b></p><p c