goe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<b>Role-Based Login System</b> – Controlled access by department, rank, and\r\nauthority level<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<b>Digital Requisition &amp; Issue Records</b> – Fully searchable and\r\ntimestamped logs<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<b>Automated Procurement Workflow</b> – Tracks items from purchase to\r\ndistribution<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span>\r\n<b>Audit &amp; Reporting Tools</b> – Instant generation of transaction\r\nhistories and compliance data<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Results &amp; Impact</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span> <b>Enhanced Operational\r\nControl</b> – Streamlined stock issuance and receipt workflows<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span>\r\n<b>Real-Time Visibility</b> – Better decision-making through updated inventory\r\ndata<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span>\r\n<b>Greater Accountability</b> – Transparent and traceable transactions<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span>\r\n<b>Audit-Ready System</b> – Compliant with internal and external oversight\r\nneeds<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span>\r\n<b>Scalable Framework</b> – Ready for future integration with mobile or\r\nregional 