\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚀</span> <b>Optimized Payroll\r\nAccuracy:</b> Eliminated manual errors and ensured timely salary disbursement.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📊</span>\r\n<b>Improved HR Efficiency:</b> Automated employee management, reducing\r\nadministrative workload.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🔗</span>\r\n<b>Regulatory Compliance Assurance:</b> Ensured adherence to labor laws and tax\r\nregulations.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🔒</span>\r\n<b>Enhanced Security &amp; Data Protection:</b> Strengthened employee data\r\nprivacy with robust security measures.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Conclusion<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Despite multiple challenges, Opus Technology successfully\r\nimplemented an advanced <b>HR &amp; Payroll Management System with Salary\r\nFixation</b> for Agrani Bank PLC. This project highlights our expertise in <b>developing\r\nsecure, scalable, and efficient enterprise solutions</b> for the banking\r\nsector.<o:p></o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📩</span> <b>Looking to optimize\r\nyour HR &amp; Payroll processes?</b> Let’s innovate together! Contact Opus\r\nTechnology today.<o:p></o:p></p>', 'agrani-bank-plc-transforming-hr-payroll-management-with-opus-technology', '2025-02-09 01:45:54', '2025-05-26 08:45:59'),
(58, 8, '6821fce93338e.png', 'Enhancing Officer Wellness: Health Service Management System for Bangladesh Police Headquarters', 'Opus Technology Limited partnered with Bangladesh Police Headquarters to implement a Health Service Management Software tailored to streamline medical services, appointment scheduling, and health record management. This digital transformation has empowered PHQ’s healthcare units to deliver faster, more coordinated, and transparent health services to police personnel and their families.', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Implementation of Health Service Management Software for\r\nBangladesh Police Headquarters with Opus Technology</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Case Study: Health Service Management System for PHQ<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Client:</b> Bangladesh Police Headquarters (PHQ)<br>\r\n<b>Delivered by:</b> Opus Technology Limited<br>\r\n<b>Client Website:</b> <a href=\"https://www.police.gov.bd/\" target=\"_new\">www.police.gov.bd</a><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p><b style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 1rem;\">Client Overview</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">The <b>Bangladesh Police\r\nHeadquarters</b> oversees health services for thousands of officers and staff\r\nstationed across the country. Its medical wing plays a critical role in\r\nproviding regular check-ups, treatment, and emergency services. Historically,\r\nthese services were managed manually, making it difficult to track\r\nappointments, manage health records, and ensure consistent care. PHQ sought a\r\ndigital solution to modernize and centralize healthcare service delivery.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Project Summary</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Opus Technology Limited developed\r\nand delivered a comprehensive <b>Health Service Management Software</b> for the\r\nPHQ, designed to automate medical recordkeeping, manage doctor appointments,\r\nstreamline prescription workflows, and improve the overall healthcare\r\nexperience for officers and staff.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Key Objectives</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">• Digitize and centralize medical records of police\r\npersonnel<br>\r\n• Streamline appointment booking and patient flow<br>\r\n• Enable real-time access to treatment history and prescriptions<br>\r\n• Improve service delivery and reduce administrative overhead<br>\r\n• Ensure data security and confidentiality in health-related records<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Challenges</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚫</span> Manual record-keeping\r\nled to misplaced or inaccessible medical data<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚫</span>\r\nNo appointment scheduling system created long wait times and confusion<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚫</span>\r\nDoctors and staff lacked access to centralized health histories<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚫</span>\r\nInefficiencies in prescription management and follow-up<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Our Solution</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Opus Technology delivered a <b>custom Health Service\r\nManagement System</b> equipped with:<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span> <b>Digital Patient Records</b>\r\n– Secure electronic health p