(65, 54, '6821e411b5188.png', 'Digitizing Lien Operations for ICB – Mobile App Solution by Opus Technology', 'Opus Technology developed and deployed a secure, cross-platform mobile application for the Investment Corporation of Bangladesh (ICB) to manage unit lien requests and releases. Designed for both Android and iOS, the solution streamlined lien processing, enhanced transparency, and empowered stakeholders with real-time access—delivering a key step in ICB’s digital transformation journey.', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📱</span> Case Study:\r\nMobile-Based Unit Lien Management System for ICB<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Client: Investment Corporation of Bangladesh (ICB)<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Industry:</b> Financial Services | <b>Solution:</b> Unit\r\nLien Management Mobile Apps (Android &amp; iOS)<br>\r\n<b>Delivered by:</b> Opus Technology Limited<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🧩</span> Client Overview</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Investment Corporation of Bangladesh (ICB)</b> is a\r\nstate-owned financial institution playing a key role in Bangladesh’s capital\r\nmarket. ICB required a modern solution to streamline and digitize the process\r\nof lien management on investment units—enabling banks, institutions, and\r\ninvestors to interact with the system in real-time and securely from mobile\r\nplatforms.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:4.0pt;line-height:107%\">&nbsp;</span><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🎯</span> Project Goals</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">To meet ICB’s modernization objectives, Opus Technology was\r\ntasked with designing and delivering <b>Unit Lien Management System Mobile Apps</b>\r\nfor both <b>Android and iOS</b>, with the following goals:<o:p></o:p></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0in\" type=\"disc\">\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\">Eliminate\r\n     manual paperwork and physical submissions for lien processing<o:p></o:p></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\">Enable\r\n     real-time unit lien requests, releases, and verifications<o:p></o:p></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\">Ensure\r\n     security, transparency, and traceability in all lien transactions<o:p></o:p></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\">Provide\r\n     mobile accessibility for stakeholders (banks, institutions, and investors)<o:p></o:p></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\">Integrate\r\n     seamlessly with ICB’s existing systems and databases<o:p></o:p></li>\r\n</ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">⚙️</span> Challenges</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🔒</span> <b>Data Security &amp;\r\nIntegrity</b> – Managing sensitive financial data over mobile channels<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🔄</span>\r\n<b>Real-Time Syncing</b> – Ensuring live updates between users and ICB’s\r\nbackend system<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📲</span>\r\n<b>Cross-Platform Development</b> – Delivering a consistent user experience\r\nacross Android and iOS<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📑</span>\r\n<b>Regulatory Compliance</b> – Meeting financial sector standards for data\r\nprivacy and record-keeping</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">✅</span> Our Solution<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Opus Technology developed and deployed <b>Unit Lien\r\nManagement System Mobile Apps</b> tailored to ICB’s specific functional and\r\nregulatory requirements. Key features included:<o:p></o:p></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0in\" type=\"disc\">\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;\">✔</span>\r\n     <b>User Authentication &amp; Role-Based Access</b> – For banks,\r\n     institutions, and ICB officials<o:p></o:p></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;\">✔</span>\r\n     <b>Lien Request &amp; Release</b> – Submission, tracking, and\r\n     approval/release workflows via app<o:p></o:p></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;\">✔</span>\r\n     <b>Real-Time Notifications</b> – Alerts for request status, approvals, and\r\n     document submission<o:p></o:p></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;\">✔</span>\r\n     <b>Integration with ICB Core System</b> – Backend synchronization for\r\n     accurate, up-to-date data<o:p></o:p></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;\">✔</span>\r\n     <b>Multi-Platform Support</b> – Native Android and iOS apps with uniform\r\n     UX</li></ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📈</span> Results &amp; Impact<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🚀</span> <b>Streamlined\r\nOperations</b> – Faster lien processing and reduced dependency on physical\r\npaperwork<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🔐</span>\r\n<b>Enhanced Security</b> – End-to-end encryption and secure login for financial\r\nintegrity<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📊</span>\r\n<b>Transparency &amp; Accountability</b> – Traceable workflows for every lien\r\ntransaction<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📱</span>\r\n<b>Anywhere Access</b> – Stakeholders can now initiate and manage liens\r\ndirectly from their smartphones<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🏁</span> Conclusion<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Opus Technology’s successful\r\ndelivery of the <b>Unit Lien Management System Mobile Apps</b> has empowered\r\nICB with a robust, secure, and mobile-first lien processing ecosystem. This\r\nproject underscores Opus Technology’s ability to deliver digital transformation\r\nin highly regulated financial environments.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">💼</span> Opus Technology –\r\nPowering Digital Finance Solutions for Government &amp; Institutions<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🔗</span> Let’s talk for