(66, 55, '6821e8ca63731.png', 'Carlcare Technology BD Ltd. – Streamlining VAT Compliance with Opus Technology', 'Opus Technology successfully delivered a customized VAT Management Software solution for Carlcare Technology BD Ltd., enabling automated tax calculations, real-time reporting, and seamless integration with their operations. This implementation empowered Carlcare to ensure regulatory compliance, reduce manual efforts, and improve financial transparency across its nationwide service centers.', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">📊</span> Case Study: VAT\r\nManagement Software Implementation for Carlcare Technology BD Ltd.<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Client:</b> Carlcare Technology BD Ltd.<br>\r\n<b>Industry:</b> Consumer Electronics &amp; After-Sales Service<br>\r\n<b>Delivered by:</b> Opus Technology Limited<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">🧾</span> Client Overview</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Carlcare Technology BD Ltd. is the official after-sales\r\nservice provider for brands like TECNO, itel, and Infinix in Bangladesh. With a\r\nnationwide service network and a high volume of transactions, Carlcare needed a\r\nreliable VAT management solution to ensure regulatory compliance, reduce manual\r\nworkload, and streamline financial reporting in line with Bangladesh’s VAT Act.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;\">⚠️</span> Challenges</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Before partnering with Opus Technology, Carlcare Technology\r\nfaced several VAT-related issues:<o:p></o:p></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0in\" type=\"disc\">\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\