(8, 'Executive – Software Sales and Marketing', 'executive-software-sales-and-marketing', 'Full Time', '2024-11-11', '2024-11-30', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal\"><b>Job Description:</b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:\r\nnone\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\ntext-align:justify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none\">The\r\nSales and Marketing Executive for Software Sales will drive revenue growth and\r\nmarket expansion in the Malaysia market. This role combines sales strategy with\r\nmarketing initiatives to build customer relationships, identify potential\r\nclients, and showcase how our software solutions meet the unique needs of\r\nvarious Malaysian industries. The executive will collaborate closely with\r\nproduct and marketing teams to craft value-driven propositions and work\r\ndirectly with prospects to convert leads into long-term partnerships.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\nline-height:normal;mso-outline-level:3\"><b>Key\r\nResponsibilities:<o:p></o:p></b></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"1\" type=\"1\">\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list .5in\"><b>Sales Strategy and Lead Generation:</b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n     mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-font-kerning:\r\n     0pt;mso-ligatures:none\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <ul type=\"circle\">\r\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\n      auto;line-height:normal;mso-list:l2 level2 lfo1;tab-stops:list 1.0in\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n      mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-font-kerning:\r\n      0pt;mso-ligatures:none\">Develop and execute sales plans focused on\r\n      identifying and acquiring new clients in Malaysia across target\r\n      industries such as finance, retail, restaurant, health, construction,\r\n      facility and manufacturing.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\n      auto;line-height:normal;mso-list:l2 level2 lfo1;tab-stops:list 1.0in\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n      mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-font-kerning:\r\n      0pt;mso-ligatures:none\">Generate and qualify leads through direct\r\n      outreach, networking, events, and digital channels.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\n      auto;line-height:normal;mso-list:l2 level2 lfo1;tab-stops:list 1.0in\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n      mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-font-kerning:\r\n      0pt;mso-ligatures:none\">Identify decision-makers and establish contact\r\n      with key stakeholders in prospective companies to build relationships and\r\n      foster trust.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n </ul>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list .5in\"><b>Client Engagement and Relationship Management:</b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n     mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-font-kerning:\r\n     0pt;mso-ligatures:none\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <ul type=\"circle\">\r\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\n      auto;line-height:normal;mso-list:l2 level2 lfo1;tab-stops:list 1.0in\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n      mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-font-kerning:\r\n      0pt;mso-ligatures:none\">Conduct product demonstrations and presentations\r\n      tailored to client needs, highlighting solution benefits and ROI.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\n      auto;line-height:normal;mso-list:l2 level2 lfo1;tab-stops:list 1.0in\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n      mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-font-kerning:\r\n      0pt;mso-ligatures:none\">Nurture and maintain relationships with\r\n      prospective and existing clients to ensure high customer satisfaction and\r\n      retention.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\n      auto;line-height:normal;mso-list:l2 level2 lfo1;tab-stops:list 1.0in\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n      mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-font-kerning:\r\n      0pt;mso-ligatures:none\">Collaborate with clients to understand their\r\n      business challenges and position our software as a tailored solution to\r\n      these needs.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n </ul>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list .5in\"><b>Market Research and Competitive Analysis