(1, 'Engr. Md. Jafar Iqbal', 'image_1743221189.png', 'MANAGING DIRECTOR & CEO', 'Engr. Md. Jafar Iqbal, the Managing Director & CEO of Opus Technology Limited, is a visionary leader with a strong background in engineering. He has driven the company’s growth with innovation and technical expertise, keeping it at the forefront of technology trends. Known for client-centricity, he fosters a culture of innovation and continuous learning within his team. His forward-thinking approach for the company for sustained success of making Opus Technology Limited.', 'Engr. Md. Jafar Iqbal, Managing Director & CEO of Opus Technology Limited, is a visionary leader with an engineering background. He drives growth through innovation, client-centricity, and a forward-thinking approach, making Opus Technology a trusted tech partner.', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; text-align: justify;\">Engr Md. Jafar Iqbal is a visionary leader and the Managing Director of Opus Technology Limited, a leading technology company. With a profound passion for innovation and a wealth of experience in the industry, he has played a pivotal role in shaping the growth and success of the organization.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; text-align: justify;\">With a strong educational background in engineering, Engr Md. Jafar Iqbal brings a solid technical foundation to his role as Managing Director. His expertise and deep understanding of technology have enabled him to drive the company’s strategic direction and spearhead initiatives that deliver cutting-edge solutions to clients.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; text-align: justify;\">Under his dynamic leadership, Opus Technology Limited has witnessed significant expansion and achieved remarkable milestones. His ability to identify emerging trends and anticipate the needs of the market has allowed the company to stay at the forefront of the rapidly evolving technology landscape.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; text-align: justify;\">Engr Md. Jafar Iqbal is known for his unwavering commitment to client satisfaction and building long-term partnerships. He believes in understanding the unique challenges faced by each client and providing tailored solutions that address their specific requirements. His emphasis on quality, reliability, and customer-centricity has earned Opus Technology Limited a reputation for excellence in the industry.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; text-align: justify;\">Beyond his professional accomplishments, Engr Md. Jafar Iqbal is highly regarded for his leadership style and his ability to inspire and motivate his team. He fosters a culture of innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning, creating an environment where employees are empowered to unleash their full potential and drive the company’s success.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; text-align: justify;\">As a forward-thinking leader, Engr Md. Jafar Iqbal is dedicated to staying abreast of the latest technological advancements and industry trends. He actively seeks opportunities to expand Opus Technology Limited’s service offerings and explore new markets, positioning the company for sustained growth and continued success.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; text-align: justify;\">Engr Md. Jafar Iqbal’s vision, expertise, and leadership have been instrumental in establishing Opus Technology Limited as a trusted technology partner for clients across diverse industries. With his guidance, the company is poised to make even greater strides in the future, delivering innovative solutions that transform businesses and drive digital transformation.</p>', 'Jafar_Iqbal', 'https://www.facebook.com/jafar.mona/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/mdjafariqbal/', '2024-05-06 01:29:52', '2025-03-29 09:06:29'),
(2, 'Bipasha Afrin', 'image_1743183883.png', 'DIRECTOR', 'Akhtar Afrin, Director at Opus Technology Limited, is an experienced professional known for her strategic leadership and deep industry understanding. With a background in computer science, she excels in client-focused innovation, driving the company’s growth. She fosters lasting client partnerships, promotes team development, and actively contributes to the technology community, making Opus Technology Limited a trusted industry player in digital transformation.', 'Akhtar Afrin, Opus Technology Limited’s Director, is an experienced leader in client-centric innovation with a computer science background. She builds strong client partnerships, develops teams, and contributes to the tech community, enhancing Opus’s reputation in digital transformation.', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; text-align: justify;\">Akhtar Afrin is a seasoned professional and serves as the Director of Opus Technology Limited, a reputable technology company. With a wealth of experience and a deep understanding of the industry, she plays a vital role in the company’s strategic planning and overall management.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; text-align: justify;\">Akhtar Afrin brings a diverse skill set to her position, combining her expertise in business strategy, technology solutions, and client management. Her exceptional leadership abilities and strategic thinking have been instrumental in driving the growth and success of Opus Technology Limited.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; text-align: justify;\">With a strong educational background in computer science and a passion for innovation, Akhtar Afrin has consistently stayed ahead of the curve in the rapidly evolving technology landscape. She has a keen eye for identifying emerging trends and leveraging them to develop cutting-edge solutions that meet the unique needs of clients.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; text-align: justify;\">Akhtar Afrin is renowned for her commitment to client satisfaction and building long-lasting partnerships. She believes in a client-centric approach, where understanding their challenges and goals is paramount. By fostering collaborative relationships, she ensures that Opus Technology Limited delivers tailored solutions that exceed client expectations.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; text-align: justify;\">As a director, Akhtar Afrin is deeply invested in the professional growth and development of her team members. She encourages a culture of continuous learning, innovation, and teamwork within the company. By nurturing a positive and empowering work environment, she enables her team to reach their full potential and deliver outstanding results.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; text-align: justify;\">Beyond her responsibilities at Opus Technology Limited, Akhtar Afrin actively contributes to the technology community. She participates in industry events, conferences, and forums, where she shares her knowledge and insights with peers and aspiring professionals. Her expertise and thought leadership have earned her recognition as a respected figure in the technology sector.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; text-align: justify;\">Akhtar Afrin’s dedication, strategic vision, and expertise have been instrumental in positioning Opus Technology Limited as a trusted technology partner. With her guidance, the company continues to push boundaries and deliver innovative solutions that drive digital transformation for clients across various industries.</p>', 'Bipasha_Afrin', 'https://www.facebook.com/bipashaafrin', 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/bipasha-afrin-640815a6/', '2024-05-06 01:30:33', '2025-03-28 22:44:43');
