(33, 13, '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: montserrat, sans-serif;\"><i>A complete end‐to‐end, scalable and pre‐configured core microfinance system that allows you to deliver exceptional microfinance services, enhance customer satisfaction and agility, fuel innovation and extend your competitive advantage through its advance technology and unique features. The solution is designed for growth as well as cost effectiveness. Opus Technology Limited offers comprehensive features to support the full spectrum of microfinance operations—from small, community‐based microfinance institutions to large deposit taking microfinance operations.</i></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.9rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: montserrat, sans-serif;\"><i>Technically advanced with most comprehensive and flexible functionality, Opus Technology Limited offers microfinance institutions a technological competitive edge that creates a unique value proposition for the customers. It supports a wide variety of finance products and services, mentioned below but not limited to only these, as Opus’ Microfinance Software is a solution that can adopt to your specific business needs and requirements.&nbsp;</i><i style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">The microfinance software enables to send the field officers to collect loan repayments and deposits in remote areas using the mobile application system. Microfinance Software Solution is a robust and scalable platform that helps to automate all business processes of organization on a single technology backbone, thereby helping to plan business growth at lower investments, enhance customer reach multi-fold in a secure manner and keep track of the profitability as well as compliance &amp; reporting</i></p></div>', 'image1743924558.jpg', '2024-05-14 08:52:10', '2025-04-06 12:30:10'),
