(131, 32, 'icon1715511493.png', 'Improved Talent Quality', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.97);\">The \"PARTNER\" Vendor Management System enhances the talent pool by providing a vendor-neutral approach that optimizes supplier options. This enables access to a wider range of high-quality talent.</span><br></p>', '2024-05-12 10:58:13', '2024-05-12 10:58:13'),
