(8, '67b40b3e29ea0.png', 'Re-engineering & Migration Services by Opus Technology', '<p data-start=\"150\" data-end=\"518\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">In today’s rapidly evolving digital landscape, legacy systems can hinder business growth. At <strong data-start=\"243\" data-end=\"262\">Opus Technology</strong>, we specialize in <strong data-start=\"281\" data-end=\"311\">Re-engineering &amp; Migration</strong> solutions, enabling enterprises to transition from outdated systems to cutting-edge technologies. </p><p data-start=\"150\" data-end=\"518\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Our approach ensures seamless transformation while maximizing efficiency, scalability, and business value.</p><h2 data-start=\"520\" data-end=\"565\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong data-start=\"1292\" data-end=\"1335\" style=\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 2rem;\">Our Re-engineering &amp; Migration Approach</strong></h2><p data-start=\"1338\" data-end=\"1770\"></p><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">✅ </span><strong data-start=\"1340\" data-end=\"1367\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Assessment &amp; Evaluation</strong><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"> – Analyzing your existing system for optimization potential</span></div><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">✅ </span><strong data-start=\"1432\" data-end=\"1456\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Technology Selection</strong><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"> – Identifying the best-fit solutions for your business</span></div><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">✅ </span><strong data-start=\"1516\" data-end=\"1560\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Need-gap Analysis &amp; Strategy Formulation</strong><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"> – Aligning technology with business goals</span></div><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">✅ </span><strong data-start=\"1607\" data-end=\"1632\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Development