(9, '67b412104d4ea.png', 'Cyber Security', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">In today’s digital world,\r\nsafeguarding your data, systems, and networks is more critical than ever. Cyber\r\nthreats are evolving rapidly, making robust security measures essential. At\r\nOpus Technology, we offer cutting-edge Cyber Security Solutions to protect\r\nagainst cyberattacks and data breaches. Our expert team ensures your business\r\nremains secure, resilient, and compliant with industry regulations. Whether you\r\nneed threat detection, risk assessment, or incident response, we tailor\r\nsolutions to fit your IT infrastructure. Partner with Opus Technology to build\r\na secure digital future—because security is not an option, it’s a necessity.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Our Security Services Include:</b><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ol><li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Network Security<o:p></o:p></li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cloud Security<o:p></o:p></li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Endpoint Security<o:p></o:p></li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Incident Response &amp; Recovery<o:p></o:p></li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Data Encryption &amp; Protection<o:p></o:p></li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Compliance &amp; Regulatory\r\nSolutions<o:p></o:p></li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Identity &amp; Access Management\r\n(IAM)<o:p></o:p></li><li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Threat Intelligence &amp;\r\nMonitoring<o:p></o:p></li></ol>', '2025-02-18 10:52:32', '2025-02-18 10:55:40');
